divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting in a local park parking lot just relaxing when i noticed a oval shaped metallic object fly in from the western sky it was flying pretty low and flying at a medium speed i could tell it was metallic because the sun shine reflected off of it i've been seeing quite a few ufos lately i have never seen too many here in iowa but they are appearing more frequently
Summary: oval metallic ufo appears after winterstorm
